{
  "stem": "13251.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so this was a dance for 18 and over, and my wife shouldn't have been there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was only 17 at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she looked older, I guess.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was, you know, developed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So Sandy brought her with her and say, hey, you know Helene.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So yeah, so we talked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I never paid any attention to her because I was 25 going on 26, and she was 17.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't give her any thought at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] In fact, she introduced me to a cousin of hers [LAUGHS] that I took out once.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was it because I didn't really care for her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But anyway, during this-- this dance-- the way they did it in Cleveland, they used to come two, three girls together, and then go home maybe with dates.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Like, you know, boys would say, can I take you home?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So just-- I had really no intention, no motivation at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "After talking with her and dancing with her, I says, do you have a ride home?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She said no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "OK, I'll take you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So she says OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So on the way home, [LAUGHS] we-- I figured, ah, give the girl a break.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I stopped at one of those hamburger places like a Bob's, said, would you like to get something to eat?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Says, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So that's where it started, OK?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So on the way home-- I take her home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I said, well, you know, it's been nice, this and that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I mean, no necking or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, she's a kid, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I say to her, just kind of kidding-- well, I didn't know what to say.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I says, well, you don't want to see me again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I'm too old for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She says, I don't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
